  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft from <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Cactus Flesh</span> and <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Star Bulbs</span>. Learn the blueprint with the aid of a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Science Specialist</span> in a base.<br>Cactus Flesh can be farmed, or found wild on <span class=\"name name-stellar\">barren planets</span>.<br>Star Bulbs can be farmed, or found wild on <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">lush planets</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "由<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">仙人掌肉</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">星辰朵</span>制作而成。在基地中，在<span class=\"name name-technology\">科学专家</span>的帮助下学习设计图。<br>仙人掌肉可以通过种植获得，也能在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">贫瘠星球</span>上找到。<br>星辰朵可以通过种植获得，也能在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">茂盛星球</span>上找到。",
    "TencentChinese": "由<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">仙人掌肉</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">星辰朵</span>制作而成。在基地中，在<span class=\"name name-technology\">科学专家</span>的帮助下学习设计图。<br>仙人掌肉可以通过种植获得，也能在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">贫瘠星球</span>上找到。<br>星辰朵可以通过种植获得，也能在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">茂盛星球</span>上找到。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "以<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">仙人掌肉</span>及<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">星球莖</span>製作。在基地裡借助<span class=\"name name-technology\">科學專家</span>來了解設計圖。<br>仙人掌肉可以在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">荒蕪星球</span>上栽種或於野外採集。<br>星球莖則可以於<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">蒼翠星球</span>上栽種或於野外採集。"
